      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/10316b5178d5109d597f415d6e7903dc_7335914184522245985.png",
                "id": "talent48883",
                "key": "Blunt Refusal",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Blunt Refusal"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, attaches <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Geo Infusion</span> to this character. <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> up to 5 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> from your Hand. Each card you <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Discard</span> causes this to deal +1 DMG, and you draw 1 card.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Geo Infusion</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span><br>The character to which this is attached has their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> dealt converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/d13eff9275ac9df191b4e1f83bdd18c7_8637538515646090418.png",
                "id": "talent15213",
                "key": "Ceremonial Crystalshot ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ceremonial Crystalshot "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Piercing DMG</span> to all opposing characters on standby. Summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rosula Dorata Salute</span> and creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> card before adding it to your Hand.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/628f95403aa06294879f92c054efe42d_1163831616996542965.png",
                "id": "talent37136",
                "key": "As the Sunlit Sky's Singing Salute ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "As the Sunlit Sky's Singing Salute "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After an opponent's character takes Crystallize reaction DMG:</span> Create 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> and randomly place them into your deck.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/7e023ac7d7c52126ccbea78e74621bfd_1717490426462036975.png",
                "id": "talent15206",
                "key": "Mutual Assistance Network ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Mutual Assistance Network "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Event Card</span></p><p>Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> to the opponent's active character and draw 1 card.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_2094167210219093724.png",
                "id": "talent33107",
                "key": "Crystal Shrapnel",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "white"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/ca5315848113a22db13d032f358ddbdb_6910452553619148070.png",
                "title": "Crystal Shrapnel"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>, draw 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Crystal Shrapnel</span> card.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_621542796279128481.png",
                "id": "talent96909",
                "key": "Rosula Dorata Salute",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/18/35428890/0e289adec71813e82ee8edc967616397_6690297044806986088.gif",
                "title": "Rosula Dorata Salute"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Reacts with Elements if they are already applied:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, your active character gains 1 Shield point (Can stack, max 2 points)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_9181298579223638142.png",
                "id": "talent83957",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Duration (Rounds)</span></strong><br>Each time you reach the end of a Round, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> -1.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Duration (Rounds)</span> runs out.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Discard</span></strong><br>Use Action Cards or Character Skill effects to Discard Action Cards from Hand or Deck.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.<br></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Piercing DMG</span></strong><br>Piercing DMG cannot be increased by any bonuses, but cannot be defended against using Shields or DMG Immunity either.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/07/16/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_432029290776212853.png",
                "id": "talent35733",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
